            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華爾街尋找牛市新引擎 高盛看好中產階級消費股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 由於擔心人工智能交易放緩，華爾街的策略師正尋找為美股牛市提供動力的新引擎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛由Ben Snider領銜的團隊將目光投向那些受益於中產階層消費者支出增加的公司。Snider團隊看好醫療服務提供商、材料生產商以及必需消費品製造商。但他們尤其看漲那些銷售「錦上添花」型商品、而非「生活必需」商品的企業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一群體包括銷售高端服裝和配飾的商店、家居用品製造商、旅行社和賭場。高盛的團隊認為，美國經濟有望加速成長，這將提振那些成長穩定但利潤率較低公司的利潤—這類股票的表現自10月以來一直跑贏。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f017e21d-c26d-3c49-8ff4-7227348add00-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與中等收入消費者支出相關的股票尤其具有吸引力，」Snider團隊在1月6日致投資者的報告中寫道。「中等收入消費者的實際收入成長將加快，這應該會轉化為銷售成長的提升。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">涵蓋Carmax、Etsy和Academy Sports &amp; Outdoors Inc.的標普零售精選行業指數今年以來上漲3.5%，自11月初假日購物旺季開始以來上漲8.8%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛的團隊預計，美國總統川普的關稅逆風減弱、勞動力市場趨穩以及政府去年立法帶來的稅款返還將提振消費者。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/evQJ0yIo8Tv6SmOgrN4XkA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/242db3be930d332bf174e0a06b80b0fa\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Sees Consumer Stocks Gaining Amid AI Valuation Worries</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E5%B0%8B%E6%89%BE%E7%89%9B%E5%B8%82%E6%96%B0%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%A2%E9%9A%8E%E7%B4%9A%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%82%A1-131118275.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-09 21:00:56",
